<br />

<br />
One last thing.. Does anyone know of a program that could do this so i could atleast try it out? went to download.com and searched Macro. and mostly came up with macro programs for typing.. so any help would be greatly appreated.. i want the auto fire, auto forage. w/o having to mess with a gamepad.. i like the mouse and keyboard set up just want the added feature of the gamepad... if that made any since</span><span class="gentblsmall"></span></td>
