			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Sorry about resurrecting a two week old thread, just wanted to toss in the Nostromo N45 as a choice. I picked one up day before yesterday, spent some time setting up the macros and what not and it simply rocks.
<br />

<br />
I like the dual analog sticks so I don't even have to use my keyboard and mouse except to chat and do stuff like move inventory around.
<br />

<br />
The N50 looked nice, but I wanted the analog inputs and for 19.99 at Fry's, it was hard to pass up <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile.gif" border="0" />.
<br />

<br />
Having four triggers is nice, too. One trigger is runs my /assist hotkey, another for auto kick, another for auto fire and one for autoattack.
<br />

<br />
I have my casting macros on the action buttons, so again, everything is right there.
<br />

<br />
It has definitely made my life easier, if only I tried them sooner <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile.gif" border="0" />.<br />_________________<br /><img src="http://archon.silvertree.org/twig_anm.gif" border="0" />
<br />
